Gen-san! Tolong!

00:12:03.330 --> 00:12:05.260
Jangan kau sentuh anak-anak itu!

00:12:05.260 --> 00:12:06.270
Kurrobi.

00:12:10.610 --> 00:12:11.450
Gen-san!

