Tidak?

00:15:40.520 --> 00:15:41.420
Katakan!

00:15:41.420 --> 00:15:42.460
Lepaskan aku!

00:15:43.150 --> 00:15:43.910
Nami…

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:45.670
Nami!

